item.description:
Cox Reservation consists of 27 acres of upland, salt marsh, farmlands with house and barn, and river frontage. The views east toward the salt Marsh , the Essex River, the back of Crane Beach, and Castlt Hill and Choates Island are Magnificent.www.ecga.org l

There is a barn on the property that should make for some nice photos. You should wear boots and  dress warm, as we will walk the property. We could also shoot in Essex, if time allows.

We may go out for food and drink after shoot.

Meet at the lot above the house by the barn at 11AM. D
item.how_to_find_us: Parking lot at top of road by house.
item.why: This will be a good time to shoot in the snow.
item.name: Winter Landscape Shoot.
